            <div class="dt-section-container"><h2 class="section-main-title section-heading-thin-border thin-left" style="color:#ffffff;border-color:#008dd6">
                Career Opportunities
            </h2>
            </div></div>
	<div class="wpb_gallery wpb_posts_slider wpb_content_element flex-slider-plain" dir="ltr">
		<div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="wpb_gallery_slides wpb_flexslider flexslider_slide flexslider" data-interval="5" data-flex_fx="slide"><ul class="slides"><li><a class="link_image" href="http://www.rekointl.com/career/deburr-handman/" title="Permalink to Deburr/Handman"><img width="300" height="157" src="http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/deburr-handman-300x157.png" class="attachment-medium" alt="Handman Job" srcset="http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/deburr-handman-300x157.png 300w, http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/deburr-handman-768x402.png 768w, http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/deburr-handman-1024x536.png 1024w, http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/deburr-handman-320x167.png 320w, http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/deburr-handman.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a><div class="flex-caption"><h2 class="post-title"><a class="link_image" href="http://www.rekointl.com/career/deburr-handman/" title="Permalink to Deburr/Handman">Deburr/Handman</a></h2><p>Cleaning, deburring, and assembling parts for a manufacturing facility.</p>
</div></li><li><a class="link_image" href="http://www.rekointl.com/career/boring-mill-operator/" title="Permalink to Boring Mill Operator"></a><div class="flex-caption"><h2 class="post-title"><a class="link_image" href="http://www.rekointl.com/career/boring-mill-operator/" title="Permalink to Boring Mill Operator">Boring Mill Operator</a></h2><p>Set-up and operate boring mill by reading and interpreting CAD data, setting up and securing work pieces and tooling, verifying machine systems and tool sequence, setting cutting tools, programming to CAD data, machining work piece, checking finished work pieces, de-burring and prepping for assembly.</p>
</div></li><li><a class="link_image" href="http://www.rekointl.com/career/material-handler-split-shift/" title="Permalink to Material Handler &#8211; Split Shift"><img width="300" height="157" src="http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/material-handler-300x157.png" class="attachment-medium" alt="Material Handler" srcset="http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/material-handler-300x157.png 300w, http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/material-handler-768x402.png 768w, http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/material-handler-1024x536.png 1024w, http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/material-handler-320x167.png 320w, http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/material-handler.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a><div class="flex-caption"><h2 class="post-title"><a class="link_image" href="http://www.rekointl.com/career/material-handler-split-shift/" title="Permalink to Material Handler &#8211; Split Shift">Material Handler &#8211; Split Shift</a></h2><p>To ensure all incoming and outgoing goods are organized, stocked throughout the plant, and inventory is tracked. This is a split shift from 11am-9:30pm.</p>
</div></li><li><a class="link_image" href="http://www.rekointl.com/career/trim-die-designer/" title="Permalink to Trim Die Designer"></a><div class="flex-caption"><h2 class="post-title"><a class="link_image" href="http://www.rekointl.com/career/trim-die-designer/" title="Permalink to Trim Die Designer">Trim Die Designer</a></h2><p>Develops a Trim Die/By-Pass Shear Die design which meets the design criteria of the customer by using the customers initial design or press specifications within the cost, timing and quality objectives.</p>
</div></li><li><a class="link_image" href="http://www.rekointl.com/career/applications-engineer/" title="Permalink to Applications Engineer"><img width="300" height="157" src="http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/applications-engineer-300x157.png" class="attachment-medium" alt="Applications Engineer" srcset="http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/applications-engineer-300x157.png 300w, http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/applications-engineer-768x402.png 768w, http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/applications-engineer-1024x536.png 1024w, http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/applications-engineer-320x167.png 320w, http://www.rekointl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/applications-engineer.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a><div class="flex-caption"><h2 class="post-title"><a class="link_image" href="http://www.rekointl.com/career/applications-engineer/" title="Permalink to Applications Engineer">Applications Engineer</a></h2><p>Responsible for the preparation of written proposals, which include conceptual drawings, costing and presentation to customers. Proposals will be prepared for various factory automation solutions for the Life Science and Food industries.</p>
</div></li></ul></div>
		</div> 
